(firstQuint)Isolated ACTH Deficiency in Patients With Hashimoto Thyroiditis.

 Many patients with Hashimoto thyroiditis who are correctly substituted with thyroid hormones have an impaired well-being.

 in some people an isolated ACTH deficiency was found.

 In this study a 1 mu g ACTH test is performed to evaluate the adrenocortical function.

.

